Yay my internet works again! My life has been pretty 
busy and pretty messed up to. Thank god the plays over,
 so I can concentrate on other things. This is my update...
yay!

Whoa, when was the last time I wrote in this? Sorry for all the people that depend on live journals to entertain theirselves...I forgot about LJ. A LOT of shyt has happened since I've wrote. The summer was the absolute best. I experienced ALOT OF THINGS if you know what I mean! HA! I got back with Marcel recently, but then even more recently broke up with him. I'm single, once again. Marcel's too much of a bestfriend to me, to be a lover.  Theater is the best like usual, Oliver is the play. November 18,19,20,21.  I put up my pimphat...I use to talk to so many men, but I gave that up. I got sick of it THAT quick. All I can say is, since July 24th, I can't get this kid out of my mind. I'm not at liberty to say, for several reasons, whom, but hes the whole package. Bestfriend AND lover. Too bad he's taken... :( Oh well, I guess I'll wait, unless someone of the same "package" comes along and sweeps me off my feet into the stars...or not, lets get realistic Jaclyn. This year is going by so fast, and I'm glad. I can't wait till I graduate, and I have a feeling I'm not alone on that one. GUESS WHAT GUYS! IVE BEEN TRYING TO GAIN WEIGHT...AND SINCE I'VE BEEN DRINKING THOSE "BOOST" DRINKS 2 WEEKS AGO I GAINED 5 POUNDS. WOOT WOOT FOR ME! Well I'll try to remember to keep posting. Thats all for now.

I am currently half awake, half asleep. Today was my last day of work till Tuesday! Woot woot! And guess who has the house all to theirself? Me of course! Daddy is going up north and leaving the house and me alllll alone! Poor me.... HELL YEAH! So whoever wants to party just call me! The only plans I have is to hangout with Andre tomorrow and then go to the foam party at eko with Marissa and Annie! Yayy! I love ya girls! Whoever wants to come with us, give me a call and we will make plans. 
Love life is going great, no attatchments, just pimpin. ha j/p

Man I just wanna bang him till the break of dawn! MMMMMMM! I could just...

FRIDAY=Alisha and I finished taping all the footage of our music video! You all know your excited to see it. It will probably be fully finished tuesday. Marissa and I hungout and went to Jehiahs house to chill, then after we hungout with Buddha and Glenn and went to Best Buy which none of us bought anything. That concludes my friday because I went to bed at 8:00 pm.

SATURDAY= I had to beg my dad to let me go to Summer Jams because my cousins graduation party was the same day. Krystal ended up calling him unexpectedly and convincing him. It was suppose to be Krystal,Marissa,Annie, and I in the car, but plans got really messed up and too confusing. Some people wanted to leave later when there would be no good seats and some people wanted to leave early. Krystal and I ended up going without Annie and Marissa because they wanted to go with Mike D and them. We ended up going with Leah,Keristen, and Jennifer Keefer. It was real fun. Thankfully, we went at the time we did because Mobb Deep came on at 3pm. We were just in time for them. The concert was real hype at the beginning but then after Method Man, it got weak. METHOD MAN SANG MY SONG! The Rockawilder. I was all jumpin up and down! lol. After, we decided to go to Belle Isle, which was a bad idea. Traffic up the ass! Trying to get out of downtown was a pain in the ass, it took us an hour to go like 2 miles. Us girls had to lure guys into letting us change lanes it was so pitiful. Finally, we got to Belle Isle and it was SOOOO packed. We would movie 3 inches every minute. But the good thing was, there was brothas to the left, brothas to the right! lol just playing! Jennifer and I were so hungry we ended up asking these guys if we could have some of their food(from barbecuing), and they said YEAH COME GET A BURGER. They were real hospitable and gave us hamburgers,chips, and drinks. We finally got out of belle isle 2 hours later, and I drove everyone home. Since I wasn't ready to go home, I went and chilled over Chris's house and then went to Taco Bell. That was one of the most fun nights I've had in a long time.

SUNDAY= FATHERS DAY! Which means stay home with Daddy and bond!

Right now I would be joining Annie and Marissa right now in dreamland, but I had to get up and wash my damn kitchen floor because I didn't earlier and I had to do it before my dad gets home today. Marissa and Annie sure look comfortable over there sleeping, I want to go back to bed! Today, I might go with Annie and Marissa to Glenns party. I don't feel like driving so hopefully I'm getting a ride with Julie. This weekend was "off the chain". I have a feeling this summer is going to be HYPE! Tomorrow I start my summer job for the school. Woot woot! Me and Alisha are going to make another unforgetable music video! Jessie Ormbsy..if you're reading this. I now know how you felt. And sorry for looking down on you otherwise.(If you don't know what I mean, I'll tell you next time I talk to you.)

FRIDAY= Hungout with ChrisP,Jacob,JordanD,Jennifer,Joe, and Irena. We hungout at Chris's and watched movies then left to go to the dollar show. We went at the late night show. Us girls got in, but the boys got carded! AHAHAHAHHAHAH! So we ended up watching the show by ourselves and the guys went home! We seen Dawn Of The Dead. Good movie, but BAD remake. Then we met up with the guys at Chris's again and went to Keefers house. We ended up walking around her neighborhood and some crackhead asked us if we wanted any weed,coke,crack lol. It was hillarious. Then we went back and I saw her brother butt ass naked and LADIES let me tell you, that boy is FOIIIIIINE. Mmm LOL. I could just... lol. I left around 4, and drove jacob home then I went home and went to sleep.

SATURDAY= AWESOME NIGHT. I hungout with Marissa all day then at night Me,Marissa,Annie, and Irena went to Eko. I was SOOOOOOOO weak at the beginning(we got there at like 10). We thought that it was going to be like that all night but 10:30 rolled around at it got hype again. I met this guy, FINALLY a decent guy at the club! And we like danced half the night together. Yes, he was black. But HE COULD DANCE! And he was all poppin his booty...for all of you that know Leon...he had a "LEON" booty lol. And he was vibrating and popping and all that other good shit. We exchanged numbers and went back dancing. Hes the first guy that I felt comfortable dancing with that I didn't know. We wouldn't be in the same dance motion, we would be changing and he would follow right with me. I'm glad I met him ha. THEN! After the club, I decided I was going to let people come over. Annie and Marissa were already going to spend the night. But then we invited Jermaine and Emmanuel and his cousins. They all came over and luckily the neighbors didn't see lol because I told them to park down the street and be VERY VERY quiet. So they came over and we all chilled and watched that soft core porn on HBO lol and Bruce Almighty. The end of the night made me kind of upset but for some careful reasons, I don't want to explain it on LJ. But out of the whole night put together I had a blast. I LOVE YOU ANNIE AND MARISSA YOU GUYS ARE THE BEST.

Had my last 2 finals, American Studies and English...which were the easiest. After school, we had rehearsal for the fitsies then I went home. Emmanuel came over and we watched OldSchool and Van Wilder, the funniest movies ever! Then my cousin came by and chilled with us. After she left, I got my fitsie outfit on and left, we picked up Sean and Krystal then went to the fitsies. 
 
The fitsies was ok. It was fun sitting next to Crystal and her sisters. ha, we were screaming. I got one award, Funniest Laugh. HhahhHAHHahahHAHh... After fitsies we went to Coney Island, almost everyone and ate. When driving home, I bumped into Gabes back end, luckily I didn't leave a big dent. Sorry Gabe! The roads were slippery as hell and my brakes skidded and wouldn't stop. Yeah, and then when I went home, they pranked me afterwards saying his mother wanted to talk to me, I was willing to give my next pay check to pay for the damage but she(THEY), wouldn't accept it. I wouldn't have gotten mad I guess if I knew everyone wasn't there and in on it, and then Jacob calling me a bitch afterwards on my voicemail. Oh well, life goes on. I had fun earlier that day so it didn't matter.
 PaYcE oUt!

Today I had finals for Algebra Trig and Chem 1, which were the hardest finals and I'm glad I got them out of the way.
Half day was sooo fun! I hungout with Krystal,Brian, and Emmanuel. We went to the mall and were there from like 12 to 5! First of all, it was the best because me and Krystal took a survey and they gave us 15 dollars for doing it! Tyte ass shyt! Another fun festivity was when we were sitting in the display outdoor table thingy, and krystal flipped forward and almost busted her head! It was hillarious!!! Had to be there, had to be there. 

   Then us girls made a bet with the guys...so we tried on bathing suits for them, and they tried on Abercrombie tight gay shirts for us(they are brothas, its torture for them HA) and we got a picture of that shyt! 

    I bought some more filas...they are green,yellow, and white. I bought red laces so I can have the jamaican colors. So now I'm going to be all jamaicaned out! Imma by more jamaican and bob marley shirts i saw next time I go. I also want this NEW Johnny Depp shirt! Its mine bitches! 

   I think Emmanuel is becoming another bestfriend...hes someone that I can be myself around and tell anything, and plus, I can be on the phone with him for a long time! Hes mah homie!

PAYCE OUT BABYCAKES

FRIDAY= Hungout with Chris,Jacob,Jordan Diehr,Jennifer Keefer,Irena,Joe. We all went to the movies and seen Secret Window with sexy Johnny Depp. It went well, besides of the numbness of my butt sitting uncomfortably in the theater. After, we went to Chris's and watched tv. We were all supposedly spending the night, besides Irena. Yes, I was cuddling and such if you haven't heard already. And just to let everyone know, and get this straight...Jacob and I are not together. We are "talking" so to speak, but not offically together. I do have feelings for him, but I just think its to soon to make it official.

SATURDAY= Graduation...My cousin and Keir's for Redford Union High School. The ceremony was pretty boring, until Keir walked across stage then Krystals family and I were screaming our heads off(He looked amazingly sexy). After, we all went to Red Lobster, and Krystals uncle(Keirs daddy), paid for us all(12 people), hes a balla! lol The food was delicious, and those bisquits were of course off tha chain like usual. After the resteraunt, we went to Keirs house and we just chilled over there and socialized. When I got home, I called up my homegirl Marissa, and we went to Chris's and we all met up at the park with Jehiah and Winston. We were in our childhood days, playin on the swings, then we went and played some bball. Then we went home.

SUNDAY= Visited my grandpa.

Sorry I haven't typed in LJ for so long(for any of those who care). I've been busy somewhat, with school,work,and track. Track has now ended so I have that weight off my back, and now I'm trying to keep my grades up for finals. Working for Corbin is the best. In the summer I'm working for WIA program and doing TV PRODUCTION where I make movies and music videos, and hopefully I get another summer job so i can make that cheddar. Right now life is the best, my job and my grades. I'm bonding with my dad again and I like someone and he likes me too. Hopefully, it goes well. I'm suppose to hangout with Jacob,Jordan Diehr,Jennifer Keefer,Irena,Chris Pusey, and Joe Clement tomorrow and go to the movies. I hope its a blast and me and you know who get closer. Ha! This is the first white guy I've liked that Pam Peters hasn't stolen away from me. Well, theres still time lol. I can't stop smiling...my face is starting to hurt because of it! I love summertime! I hope this summer will be fun and party central. Ahh! I love you all. I'll try to keep you guys updated from now on.

PAaYyCe, Jackie

This weekend I had the house to myself once again. 

FRIDAY=Hungout with Krystal and went to go get a cd player for my car.

SATURDAY= Track meet...which was tiring as hell. I almost threw up during when I was running. Right after the meet me and Krystal left and I took back the cd player because I decided to save my money to get a better one. After, I went home, washed up to get ready to go to the movies with Chris Skupny. We went to AMC 30 which was an awful choice because they are such assholes there and they will card even a 30 year old. We wanted to see Girl Next Door, but since I wasn't 17, we had to go see 13 going on 30, which turned out to be a very cute movie. I had a really fun time with Mr. Skupny because we haven't hungout in a long time. After he dropped me off I got right in my car and drove straight to Marissas. We were calling up people to see if anyone wanted to go to the club with us. Alisha was suppose to go but she had "other plans"(HAHA ALISHA!). We were already meeting Jehiah,Emmanuel,Jermaine, and Chris P there so we just decided to go alone. When we got there it was packed and all you seen was half naked 14 year olds and rapist looking arab guys. We hungout with Leon for a little, and then finally found the crew. We were all battling in dancing. It was THEE BEST! Then me and Marissa went to go get our freak on on the dance floor. We ended up in the middle of all these chaldean guys and like got sandwiched which was the worst mistake ever. It seemed that Chaldean guys thought dancing with a girl was another way of hitting a girl from the back. THESE GUYS WERE PELVIC THRUSTING YOUR ASS AS HARD AS THEY COULD. One guy banged Marissa so hard that she tripped forward! It was hillarious! Then later on I found out the one guy I was dancing with was a Jacob Shukri look alike :(. Then...this big huge hairy arab man kept trying to dance with me. I'd see him out of the corner of my eye watching my ass and getting ready to pounce and as soon as I'd see him make a step closer I would briskly walk away. Finally, when me and Marissa were about to sandwich a decent chaldean here comes the big arab again so I RAN away and almost tripped off the dance floor lol. I had a lot of fun dancing with Emmanuel and Jehiah! They know how to boogie down! We were all making up these routines and stuff. Marissa danced on stage! She was soo cute! She was all droppin it like its hot. THIS DAY WAS ONE OF THE BEST DAYS OF MY LIFE! I need to go to the club more often. FOSHO. We left and got home about 2 and Marissa spent the night.

SUNDAY=Since Marissa spent the night, we spent pretty much the whole day together. We got up and went to KFC, rented VAMPIRES IN BROOKLYN, and went back to my place and watched it. After that, we went to the mall and went "shopping", then returned home and made Smoothies and watched more movies. MARISSA! I JUST CANT LOOK AT ANOTHER CHALDEAN BOY AGAIN! LOL! I LOVE YOU GIRL!

FORENSICS
Up the DownStaircase is going to states! We made alternate(6th place), so we get to get that free hotel room playa!
We also placed an At Large Bid, which tries to explain WHY we should still compete(as in if we did good all season). Now since I found out 2 of our multiple people probably won't go, that was an idiot thing to do(At Large). I'm just glad we get that free hotel room and we get to go watch all the multiples. Thats all I want.

THE PLAY: UP THE DOWN STAIRCASE
Well...I guess you can say we are still rehearsing for it..if you call it rehearsing. Its not going to well. Most of us still haven't memorized our lines. Crisis is going on between leads, and the play is like in 2 weeks. Oh by the way, I'm Rachel Gordan in the play. I'm basically a bitch to the teacher all the time. The play is:
THURSDAY, MAY 6
FRIDAY, MAY 7
SATURDAY, MAY 8
7:30pm in the Fitzgerald Auditorium.
ADULT= $5
STUDENT=$3

TODAY
Today was a fun day. We had an assembly with THE ONE MAN VOLLEYBALL TEAM, which was pretty neato. After school, we had a track meet. The boys wooped New Haven, but us girls got whooped by them. Why do we always have track meets on the coldest days? I mean, come on now! After the track meet, me and a whole bunch of people went to the seminar thingy at 7 which was with the volleyball guy again and he went against all the fitz kids there...he still beat us. 

OH AND GUESS WHAT GUYS! I have a new crush! I bet you'll never guess! Here's a hint: He has the most beautiful smile(it makes me want to cream myself ahha).

I haven't updated this in awhile so I'm going to start off from last weekend. LAST WEEKEND WAS OFF THE CHAIN! My father went away up north so I had the house ALL to myself!

FRIDAY= Julies Bday party. First we went to laser tag. My code name: Bob Marley. It was the funnest thing ever. That was my first time ever playing. And then Marissas car broke down, but I fixed it! Yay me. After that, we went to Mongolian barbecue which was my also first experience. The food was EXCELLENT! I love how YOU get to pick your food. 

SATURDAY= Hungout with Marissa for a little. Then hungout with Krystal, Sean, and *Keir*. It was one of the best times I've had in a LONG time. First, we went to the movies at the Phoenix. We went and seen Kill Bill Volume 2. Keir and I weren't really interested so we snuck into the Punisher(which by the way was AWESOME), and watched towards the end of the movie. Then we went back in Kill Bill. That movie was pretty good but needed more action in my point of view. After the movies we went to Taco Bell then came back to my house to eat it. Keir and I went upstairs and just CUDDLED under my covers. I still kind of like Keir. Its just hes the one guy I feel so comfortable with and someone I don't have to be "reserved" around. After we hungout at my house, we drove up to the Butterfly and played some pool. It was fun with just us four but then new visitors came. Then after the butterfly, we just drove around and talked. We were about to go up to another arcade on 8mile, but Krystals mom wanted us to come home.

SUNDAY= Went to a family barbecue, ate, then left. After I left the barbecue, I went straight to Krystals. From there we went to JEEPERS at Northland. That place is the greatest. We were all riding the rides! Then Krystals Uncles wife gave us like so many tokens we never ran out! Me and Keir got so many tickets and I just gave mine to him because there was nothing really there. He ended up with like 2,200 and somethin tickets and bought me a bracelet(the blue and clear one I wear). Its great...so now when someone comments on the bracelet, I reply: "GURRRLL/BOIII, DIS WAS 200 TICKETS!" Haha. My boo gamee dis! lol.
